===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun}}

# The conclusive [[victory]] in a game of [[chess]] that occurs when an opponent's [[king]] is [[threaten]]ed with unavoidable [[capture]].
# {{lb|en|figuratively|by extension}} Any losing situation with no [[escape]]; utter defeat.

